- Dockerfile: multi-stage build producing minimal CPU verifier image
- verify.sh: one-command verification of (model, seed, prompt) → output
- README: quick start, example seeds, technical overview

Example verified seeds (qwen2.5-3b Q4_K_M, temp=0.7):
  seed=2024: "Once upon a time, a little mouse used to go to the cinema..."
  seed=42:   "Once upon a time, there was a boy named Ivan..."
  seed=777:  "Once upon a time, there was a king who had a problem..."

